@startuml
title Diagrama de Classes - Vida / Cura / Morte\nUS-18, US-19, US-20 | v1

skinparam packageStyle rectangle

class Health {
  - currentHp : int
  - maxHp : int

  + takeDamage(amount : int)
  + heal(amount : int)
  - checkDeath()
  + die()
}

class HealingItem {
  - healAmount : int
  + apply(target : Health)
}

class DamageEvent {
  - damageAmount : int
  + apply(target : Health)
}

HealingItem --> Health : cura
DamageEvent --> Health : causa dano

note right of Health
takeDamage() chama checkDeath()
checkDeath() chama die() se HP <= 0
end note

@enduml